text: Aurangabad Bangar is a census town in Mathura district in the state of Uttar Pradesh, India. ==Geography== Aurangabad Bangar is located at . ==Demographics== India census, Aurangabad Bangar had a population of 8,819. Males constitute 53% of the population and females 47%. Aurangabad Bangar has an average literacy rate of 62%, higher than the national average of 59.5%; with 60% of the males and 40% of females literate. 19% of the population is under 6 years of age. ==References== Category:Cities and towns in Mathura district
